   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Keep Clean Water Flowing at China&apos;s Orphanages</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Splash&apos;s goal in China is to ensure clean water for every orphanage in China. Thanks to support from people like you, we achieved this momentous goal in December 2017!   But our work doesn&apos;t stop there. Splash guarantees 5-10 years of  maintenance and spare parts for each site. We&apos;re working hard to build a sustainability model to ensure safe water remains for all Chinese orphanages through local, independent management of Splash filtration systems. We need your help to keep water flowing!</narrative>
  </description>
